Connect to the above MySQL server with the 'mysql' tool, 
and find the number of records returned 
when doing a 'Union' of all records in the 'employees' table 
and all records in the 'departments' table.

mysql -u root -h (target) -P (target) -p 
Enter Password: password

show databases;

use employees;

show tables;

select * from employees LIMIT 5;
select * from departments LIMIT 5;
select dept_no from departments UNION select emp_no from employees;

663

